headline: Welltower Announces Date of Fourth Quarter 2025 Earnings Release, Conference Call and Webcast
summary: WelltowerÂ® Inc. (NYSE: WELL) today announced it will release fourth quarter 2025 financial results after the close of trading on the New York Stock Exchange on Tuesday, February 10, 2026. The Company will host a conference call and webcast on Wednesday, February 11, 2026, at 9:00 a.m. ET to discuss these results. The Company's earnings release will be available in the Investor Relations section of the Company's website.
